%C Driver for Ambarella SPI controllers

Syntax:
    spi-ambarella -C [channel number]
    spi-ambarella -S

Options (to override autodetected defaults):

    C,              Indicates SPI master device, followed by the channel number
    S,              Indicates SPI slave device

Examples:
    # Start SPI master channel 2 device ....
    spi-ambarella -C 2
    # Start SPI slave device ....
    spi-ambarella -S

